{"tid":1978561,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"李柱銘俾人拉 唔係拉一個前議員咁簡單 係象徵住香港會由軍政府變維吾爾族式恐懼統治","createTime":"2020-04-18T19:49:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-18T21:47:53.000Z","uid":151057,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"507bdcffcaf98a0f9fb66dd8b10dab92c43bc3b8","tid":1978561,"uid":151057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T19:49:37.000Z","msg":"佢唔單止負責過前基本法起草、仲係御用大律師<br />\n亦係香港史上第一個華人民主派人士 建立民主黨<br />\n要數民主派江湖地位佢應該係全香港最高果個<br />\n不但中國英國認可<br />\n甚至美國總統都邀請過同佢會面<br />\n連中國加入世貿都有份幫手游說<br />\n<br />\n呢件事代表中國政府同你哋講<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">從今日開始 中國一步都唔會讓<br />\n你唔洗再諗住任何訴求<br />\n全部都會消滅你</span></span><br />\n亦唔會好再扮下嘢同民主派商量下政改方案<br />\n<br />\n嚟緊我哋就會體會到維吾爾族人嘅感受<br />\nAre you ready?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n敵人已經想消滅你<br />\n你會唔會企起身 <br />\n捨棄所謂道德同約束<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">全民勇武 和勇不分</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定繼續俾人分化或者share post當幫咗手？"},{"pid":"593a94e3bea60b0f6b411227b27d53ae552c3577","tid":1978561,"uid":151057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T20:04:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebcee9f4a631116d7b91f5c57df1711056dcbb52","tid":1978561,"uid":154054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T20:05:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71f1a339ddde193ac848f584cdde405486edc845","tid":1978561,"uid":36065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T20:06:01.000Z","msg":"全民勇武 和勇不分 <br />\n同全民罷工一樣難"},{"pid":"887e0a309870c6bb2c86fef0f2acd661fdeeaaa0","tid":1978561,"uid":151057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71f1a339ddde193ac848f584cdde405486edc845","tid":1978561,"uid":36065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T20:06:01.000Z","msg":"全民勇武 和勇不分 <br />\n同全民罷工一樣難"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T20:29:29.000Z","msg":"香港人就死啦"},{"pid":"0d10532a7de116fc1ac1309a751c81767a83deef","tid":1978561,"uid":92188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T20:32:59.000Z","msg":"都唔係今日，我地最終都係集中營見架啦"},{"pid":"ac6591ddf7bafa04a2607952d3fa53dc88faaf99","tid":1978561,"uid":258345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T21:47:53.000Z","msg":"我相信中共內憂問題過大<br />\n必需用更嚴重既外患平衡<br />\n<br />\n捉李柱銘會出事係心知肚明<br />\n因為香港係完美既外患"}]}